    <h1 class="article-top-box-data-title">
        Expert reverses course, says Trump's ‘most pro-Israel president ever’
    </h1>

   

    <h2 class="article-top-box-data-teaser">
        But on January 30, in the aftermath of his discussion on the Wall Street Journal column with Ambassador to Israel David Friedman, Pipes wrote that Trump is “the most pro-Israel president ever".
    </h2>
    <div class="article-top-box-data-time-reporter">
        <span class="article-top-box-data-reporter-lbl-by">By </span><a rel="author" href="https://www.jpost.com/Author/Meyer-Shimon" target="_blank">Meyer Shimon</a>
    </div>

    <div class="article-top-box-data-time-reporter date-time">
        February 3, 2019 20:39
    </div>

     <span class="article-top-box-data-print-icon">
